<div class="page_header"><span class="page_header_span">Nighthaunt</span></div>
<div class="noprint">

</div>
<!--/noindex-->
<p class="legend ShowFluff">A fell wind is rising. From the darkest pits of Shyish, the Realm of Death, comes a storm of ethereal figures. An eerie mist spreads before them, blotting out the sun. They muster upon corpsestrewn battlefields or ancient burial grounds, a ghostly army of phantoms. They are the supernatural, the dead, the damned – the Nighthaunts.</p>
This page contains all of the rules you need to field your Nighthaunt miniatures on the battlefields of the Mortal Realms, from a host of exciting allegiance abilities to a range of warscrolls and warscroll battalions. The rules are split into the following sections.<ul></ul>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;"><div class="BreakInsideAvoid Corner3" style="padding:0px;max-width:988px;"><table class="frameDark collapse" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" ><tbody><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_1.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_2.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_3.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_8.png" style="width:20px"></td><td bgcolor="#1d190d" style="color:#fefefe"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif; font-size:1em"><div class="contents_header">Contents</div><div class="NavColumns3"><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt#Books" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>ooks</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt#Designers-Commentary" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">D</b>esigners’ Commentary</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt#Battletome:-Nighthaunt" style="color:#fefefe">Battletome: Nighthaunt</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Allies" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">A</b>llies</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Battle-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>attle Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Aura-of-Dread" style="color:#fefefe">Aura of Dread</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Deathless-Spirits" style="color:#fefefe">Deathless Spirits</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#From-the-Underworlds-They-Come" style="color:#fefefe">From the Underworlds They Come</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Feed-on-Terror" style="color:#fefefe">Feed on Terror</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Wave-of-Terror" style="color:#fefefe">Wave of Terror</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Spectral-Summons" style="color:#fefefe">Spectral Summons</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Returning-Slain-Models" style="color:#fefefe">Returning Slain Models</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Command-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">C</b>ommand Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Shades-of-Death" style="color:#fefefe">Shades of Death</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Artefacts-of-Power" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">A</b>rtefacts of Power</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Weapons-of-the-Damned" style="color:#fefefe">Weapons of the Damned</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Relics-of-the-Underworlds" style="color:#fefefe">Relics of the Underworlds</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Infernal-Lanterns" style="color:#fefefe">Infernal Lanterns</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Spell-Lores" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">S</b>pell Lores</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Lore-of-the-Underworlds" style="color:#fefefe">Lore of the Underworlds</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Battleplans" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>attleplans</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Death-from-Within" style="color:#fefefe">Death from Within</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Path-to-Glory" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">P</b>ath to Glory</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Nighthaunt-Warband-Tables" style="color:#fefefe">Nighthaunt Warband Tables</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Followers Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/nighthaunt/#Champion-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Champion Rewards Table</a></div></div></span></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_4.png" style="width:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_7.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_6.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_5.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
